{"tid":1402984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 咪撚再比人帶風向 不割蓆不分化","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:49:11.000Z","uid":263699,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e6fd2140ef961f45b12f3eea32a98b89bbf959","tid":1402984,"uid":263699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"發完夢返到屋企<br />\n見到啲屌前線既post<br />\n我唔知你地班人係真係咁諗定點<br />\n但一直以黎都話不割蓆不分化呀<br />\n之前見到個巴打講咗一句說話 我好認同<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線 留低  支持<br />\n前線 離開 尊重</span></span><br />\n無論點<br />\n第一個食彈<br />\n第一個俾人打<br />\n第一個俾人拉<br />\n都係前線班手足<br />\n咪撚再屌我地班手足<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">團結一致 香港先會有得救</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"f8f36da6ca58a2edadc37eab8a375bd4f703e6ac","tid":1402984,"uid":263699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:26:45.000Z","msg":"推比班手足睇"},{"pid":"214dbd2fa556509bb414c7e95edd7c6449e028da","tid":1402984,"uid":263699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"晤好再比人帶風向"},{"pid":"434a08786dc77cde3d103d608302aab8001e50b2","tid":1402984,"uid":134854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:27:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c148b3736b591acd1a6ecac297c4de572599d50","tid":1402984,"uid":263699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:28:09.000Z","msg":"鼓勵下前線呀"},{"pid":"7d3fe201009601e0b073b2d0dc029aa2dbc3fd8f","tid":1402984,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:28:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc